{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a section that allows me to make two seperate photo of the product to feature before and after. the section should allow for the title to have a customizable color picker., The images should share the same frame and a scrollable bar that is placed vertically should reveal the image when dragged to the right and left., Instead of the circle slider Use a line. Keep the circle and when I move the circle put a fireworks effects. 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
